242
0:13:35.759,000 --> 0:13:39,000
la jalousie, la possession, l'agression, le pouvoir, la dominance,

243
0:13:39.888,000 --> 0:13:4,000
les cochonneries, la malice.

244
0:13:41.676,000 --> 0:13:44,000
